@ThinkingandTinkering Thank you. I was trying to see where I should have gone to see your livestream. But, I figured it out :)

Typically, when someone has an event, they create a web page to send everyone so they know how to participate.

This is also good for you because you can ask for email addresses. These can be used to build an email newsletter. This is always a good idea because your brand is at risk if your business is built on "rented space". (Let me know if you want clarification on that).
